Borden Inc said it plans to issue up to250 mln dlrs of long-term debt securities in order tocapitalize on sharply lower interest rates.    Proceeds will be used primarily to refinance existingcommercial paper.    The company said the offering of long-term debt will be inaddition to its previously announced offering of a masterlimited partnership interest relating to Borden's basicchemicals and plastics operations. Reuter&#3;